---
layout: base.njk
---
{% set inst = instruments | instrument(instrumentId) %}
<h1>{{ inst.title }}</h1>

<div class="callout statute recorded-controls">
  <p><span class="k">Unofficial reading copy.</span> This is a text version of the recorded instrument, provided for readability and accessibility. The <strong>authoritative version is the recorded instrument</strong> on file with the Hays County Clerk — Doc. No. <strong>{{ inst.docNo }}</strong>, Official Public Records of Hays County, Texas{% if inst.opr != "—" %} ({{ inst.opr }}){% endif %}. If this copy and the recorded instrument differ, the <strong>recorded instrument controls</strong>.</p>
  <p class="inst-links">
    <a class="btn" href="{{ inst.pdf }}">Recorded PDF</a>
    <a class="btn" href="{{ inst.county }}" rel="noopener">Hays County record ↗</a>
    <a class="btn ghost" href="/governing-documents/">All governing documents</a>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="reading">
{{ content | safe }}
</div>

<hr>
<p class="note"><a href="/governing-documents/">← Back to Governing Documents</a></p>
